doc.previous: Afriqiyah Airways plans to introduce new services to Marseille.[22] Three A330s that were delivered in 2009 were used to inaugurate new routes to Dhaka, Johannesburg and Kinshasa.[22] In the winter 2010, two new routes were added to the airline's network - Beijing and Nouakchott.[23]
